replies.body: thanks for the suggestions :) ill try my best to do all

I had no idea what this nail art business was but it turns out these are super cute! 

Keep it up, I look forward to seeing what you come up with next.

Speaking of which, it would be rad if {{champion:427}} and Daisy and some lil critters were all chilling out in a forest or something.
